<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n10056b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10056b">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10056b"> 56(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> dogs of war</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Depuis quelques ann&eacute;es, on dresse et on utilise, en Allemagne, les <i>chiens de guerre</i> pour le service de s&ucirc;ret&eacute; et d&apos;exploration; leur fonction doit &ecirc;tre d&apos;aller des postes avanc&eacute;s d&eacute;tach&eacute;s d&apos;un corps arm&eacute;e &agrave; la portion principale de ce corps, et vice versa. <font color="green">[For some years war-dogs have been trained and used in Germany, in the service of safety and of reconnaisance; their function must be to go from advanced stations separated from the army corps to the main part of the corps, and vice versa.]</font> <small> Eug&egrave;ne Gallois, <a name="EGLP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#EGLP"><cite title="source">La Poste</cite></a> (1894) 174</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
